Time_Sensitive_Logic: No explicit time-based conditions in the contract.

Conditional_Logic_Paths.Withdraw_Function: Validates that only the owner can withdraw funds.
Conditional_Logic_Paths.Command_Function: Only the owner can execute commands with external contracts. The execution does not check for successful execution of external calls.
Conditional_Logic_Paths.Multiplicate_Function: Only allows funds transfer if msg.value is greater than or equal to the contract balance, else it halts.
